---
import profile from "../assets/images/profile.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { Card, CardHeader, CardContent } from "./ui/card";
---

<section class="min-h-screen py-8">
  <h1 class="mb-20">About Me</h1>
  <div class="flex w-full gap-6 h-150 items-center justify-center">
    <div class="flex-1 w-full bg-white rounded-lg pt-4">
      <Image
        class="w-100 h-150 object-cover backdrop-blur-2xl mx-auto"
        src={profile}
        alt="profile picture"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 flex-col p-6">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold text-end md:my-18">
        Engineer by training.<br />
        <span class="italic">Founder by conviction.</span>
        <br />Builder for Africa.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-start">
        I'm Blessing Kodze a software engineer and founder from Johannesburg,
        South Africa.<br /><br /> I hold a Computer Science Honours degree from the
        University of the Witwatersrand (2025), where I spent a year deep in research
        comparing Mamba state-space models against leading transformer architectures
        for financial forecasting across 8 datasets, including South African emerging
        market data. Mamba won 87.5% of the time. That kind of rigour is what I bring
        to everything I build.<br /><br /> I don't just write code I engineer products.
        From pixel-precise animated frontends to full stack SaaS systems to AI pipelines,
        I work across the stack with the same standard throughout. I care about performance,
        design, and outcomes not just shipping
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex gap-4 md:mt-20 justify-around items-center">
    <Card className="w-full md:max-w-lg">
      <CardHeader className="text-2xl font-semibold">dossier</CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>
          Founder of dossier, a FICA compliance platform for South African legal
          practitioners — built on a multi-tenant SaaS architecture with a
          RAG-based AI pipeline using LangChain, ChromaDB, and FastAPI.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card><Card className="w-full md:max-w-lg">
      <CardHeader className="text-2xl font-semibold">bleko</CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>
          Founder of bleko, a web design and digital systems agency helping
          South African SMEs get serious about their digital presence, beyond
          templates, into real infrastructure.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <div class="my-10 py-10 max-w-4xl text-center mx-auto text-2xl">
    <blockquote class="text-justify">
      <span class="italic text-4xl">"</span>My work is grounded in a simple
      belief: Africa deserves world class software. Not adapted versions of what
      works elsewhere, products built intentionally for the realities of this
      continent. That conviction shapes every project I take on.<span
        class="italic text-4xl">"</span
      >
    </blockquote>
  </div>
  <div></div>
</section>
